My Guest Tonight  with Annika Larsen is a weekly show that explores the lives of extraordinary people. We know the name, but do we know the person? My Guest Tonight  with Annika Larsen is a weekly show that explores the lives of extraordinary people. Larsen is a veteran journalist. She interviews newsmakers, influencers and innovators on their home turf, taking viewers on a journey to discover the truth behind the brand. Irreverent and undaunted, she asks the questions you always wanted answered. Where they came from and how they got here. What drives them. Their successes. And their skeletons. A first in SA, this is a show about the exceptional – good and the bad. Wednesdays at 10PM